data.description: LOOKING FOR:  A home that feels like it has ease of living on one level plus has amenities that include Swimming Pool and Building fenced in with parking area. Behind the pool is a picnic area and place to walk and play.  Two entrances and sidewalks and street lights.  New solid surface flooring (no carpet), Shower in Master Bath, Roof ( 2022) Dimensional with Ridge Vent.  The ceilings are vaulted, trey to give SO MUCH CHARACTER.  Two Car Garage to not get wet when bringing in the groceries.  Plus you have side walks for enjoying the community along with the pool, and grass area for picnic's and playing.
